main event: A UFO sighting was reported in Sherman, Texas during the summer of 1965, notable for its unusual characteristics.
interesting points: The sighting received significant publicity at the time and led to numerous inquiries afterward., The document states that it was one of the more puzzling and interesting UFO reports., There were mentions of the object being shapeless and resembling a swarm of insects., The sighting was reported to have occurred at approximately 7:35 PM., The report indicated that the object made a U-turn before descending.
sighted object: a shapeless object resembling a swarm of insects
witness description: The witness reported observing the object at 7:35 PM.
